    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"#### Key Insights - Monthly Sales Trend\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **Aggresive growth (2017):** From January 2017 to October 2017, the platform experienced **stable, nearly linear revenue growth** - surging from a level of **100k BRL** to over **600k BRL**.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **The Black Friday Spike (2017-11):** In November 2017, there is a massive, sharp peak where revenue almost touched the **1M BRL** mark. This represents the absolute historical record for the platform due to seasonal Black Friday promotions.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **Post-Holiday Stabilization (2018):** After a typical December drop, the revenue in 2018 shifted from aggressive growth into a **high-volume plateau**, stabilizing consistently between **850k BRL and 1M BRL** per month until August 2018.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **Methodological Data Cutoff (August 2018):** The timeline intentionally excludes September and October 2018. In the raw Olist dataset, these trailing months contain incomplete order records, which causes a artificial, near-zero drop on a full timeline. To prevent this technical distortion from showing a false business collapse, the data was strictly filtered to end at August 2018, ensuring a clean and accurate view of the revenue plateau.\\n\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"14aca7644c30f63\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 1.2 Top Product Categories\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Business Question:** What are the top product categories in terms of order volume and total revenue?\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"3fa61e39829b04b6\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {\n",
    "    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n",
    "     \"end_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:38:54.601561Z\",\n",
    "     \"start_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:38:53.010416Z\"\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   },\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"query_volume='''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"SELECT\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    COALESCE(t.product_category_name_english, p.product_category_name) AS category,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    COUNT(oi.order_item_id) AS order_volume\\n\",\n",
    "    \"FROM order_items oi\\n\",\n",
    "    \"JOIN orders o on oi.order_id = o.order_id\\n\",\n",
    "    \"JOIN products p on oi.product_id = p.product_id\\n\",\n",
    "    \"LEFT JOIN translation t ON p.product_category_name = t.product_category_name\\n\",\n",
    "    \"WHERE o.order_status = 'delivered'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"GROUP BY category\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ORDER BY order_volume DESC\\n\",\n",
    "    \"LIMIT 10;\\n\",\n",
    "    \"'''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"query_revenue='''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"SELECT\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    COALESCE(t.product_category_name_english, p.product_category_name) AS category,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    SUM(oi.price) AS total_revenue\\n\",\n",
    "    \"FROM order_items oi\\n\",\n",
    "    \"JOIN orders o on oi.order_id = o.order_id\\n\",\n",
    "    \"JOIN products p on oi.product_id = p.product_id\\n\",\n",
    "    \"LEFT JOIN translation t ON p.product_category_name = t.product_category_name\\n\",\n",
    "    \"WHERE o.order_status = 'delivered'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"GROUP BY category\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ORDER BY total_revenue DESC\\n\",\n",
    "    \"LIMIT 10;\\n\",\n",
    "    \"'''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"df_volume=pd.read_sql(query_volume, engine)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"df_revenue=pd.read_sql(query_revenue, engine)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(df_volume.head())\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(df_revenue.head())\\n\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"854ce59f5901a915\",\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [\n",
    "    {\n",
    "     \"name\": \"stdout\",\n",
    "     \"output_type\": \"stream\",\n",
    "     \"text\": [\n",
    "      \"                category  order_volume\\n\",\n",
    "      \"0         Bed Bath Table         10953\\n\",\n",
    "      \"1          Health Beauty          9465\\n\",\n",
    "      \"2         Sports Leisure          8431\\n\",\n",
    "      \"3        Furniture Decor          8160\\n\",\n",
    "      \"4  Computers Accessories          7644\\n\",\n",
    "      \"                category  total_revenue\\n\",\n",
    "      \"0          Health Beauty     1233131.72\\n\",\n",
    "      \"1          Watches Gifts     1166176.98\\n\",\n",
    "      \"2         Bed Bath Table     1023434.76\\n\",\n",
    "      \"3         Sports Leisure      954852.55\\n\",\n",
    "      \"4  Computers Accessories      888724.61\\n\"\n",
    "     ]\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": 88\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {\n",
    "    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n",
    "     \"end_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:37:46.682236Z\",\n",
    "     \"start_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:37:45.793744Z\"\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   },\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 8))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"sns.barplot(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    x='order_volume',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    y='category',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    hue='category',\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    data=df_volume,\\n\",\n",
