    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### Key Insights - Top Product Categories (Volume vs. Revenue)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **The Transactional Leader:** `Bed Bath Table`  is the absolute volume driver on the platform, ranking #1 in units sold. However, it drops to #3 in total revenue, showing it relies heavily on high-frequency, mid-to-low ticket sales.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **The High-Value Heavyweight:** `Health Beauty` is the ultimate crown jewel for Olist. It holds a strong #3 position in order volume but completely dominates as the #1 driver of **Total Revenue**, indicating a perfect mix of high demand and solid average ticket prices.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **Pure Premium Players:** Categories like `Watches Gifts` perfectly showcase the high-AOV (Average Order Value) effect. It ranks much lower at #7 in volume, but skyrockets to **#2 in total revenue**, proving that fewer transactions of premium goods heavily scale the platform's GMV.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **The Hidden Revenue Drivers:** By decoupling volume and revenue into two separate queries, we successfully uncovered categories like `Cool Stuff` and `Toys` on the revenue leaderboard. These categories don't move enough units to enter the top volume tier, but their high product values make them essential financial pillars for the marketplace.\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e90c193564d9a539\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 1.3 Payment Method Analysis\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Business Question:** Which payment methods are most preferred by customers, and what is their share of total revenue?\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"6d72697f04cff046\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {\n",
    "    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n",
    "     \"end_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:29:09.309378Z\",\n",
    "     \"start_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:29:08.469944Z\"\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   },\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"query = '''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"SELECT\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    pa.payment_type,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    COUNT(pa.order_id) as payment_count,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    SUM(pa.payment_value) as total_revenue\\n\",\n",
    "    \"FROM payments pa\\n\",\n",
    "    \"JOIN orders o on o.order_id=pa.order_id\\n\",\n",
    "    \"WHERE o.order_status = 'delivered'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"AND pa.payment_value != 'not_defined'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"GROUP BY payment_type\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;\\n\",\n",
    "    \"'''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"df_payments = pd.read_sql(query, engine)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"df_payments.head()\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
