    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### Key Insights - Freight vs. Product Value Analysis\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **The Logistics Equalizer:** A major analytical finding is that the `Average Freight Cost` remains remarkably flat and consistent (hovering tightly between **15 and 22 BRL**) across all top 10 categories. This indicates that courier pricing on Olist is heavily driven by standard package dimensions and baseline carrier rates rather than the underlying financial value of the goods being shipped.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **The Premium Multiplier:** `Watches Gifts` emerges as the most logistically efficient category for margins. It commands the highest `Average Product Value` at **200 BRL** while requiring one of the lowest average freight costs (~16 BRL). This low freight-to-product-value ratio explains why it serves as a massive revenue engine for the marketplace despite lower unit volumes.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **High-Burden Categories:** Lower-ticket sectors like `Telephony` (~71 BRL product value) and `Furniture Decor` exhibit a much higher logistics cost ratio. For these categories, freight eats up roughly **20-25% of the total order value**, creating a potential psychological barrier for price-sensitive customers during checkout.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"* **Operational Cushion:** High-value categories like `Auto` (~140 BRL) and `Health Beauty` ( ~130 BRL) easily absorb the baseline shipping costs, making them highly profitable avenues for promotional bundles (e.g., \\\"Free Shipping over 100 BRL\\\") to further accelerate GMV.\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"40453bb515fe3e1a\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 2.3 Delivery Time vs. Customer Satisfaction\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Business Question:** How does delivery time impact customer review scores?\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
    "   \"id\": \"2d26e56f378e379f\"\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {\n",
    "    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n",
    "     \"end_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:29:13.008890Z\",\n",
    "     \"start_time\": \"2026-07-07T18:29:12.397360Z\"\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   },\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"query='''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"SELECT\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    r.review_score,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    AVG(julianday(o.order_delivered_customer_date) - julianday(o.order_purchase_timestamp)) AS delivery_time\\n\",\n",
    "    \"FROM reviews r\\n\",\n",
    "    \"JOIN orders o on o.order_id=r.order_id\\n\",\n",
    "    \"WHERE o.order_status = 'delivered'\\n\",\n",
    "    \"GROUP BY r.review_score\\n\",\n",
    "    \"ORDER BY r.review_score desc ;\\n\",\n",
    "    \"'''\\n\",\n",
    "    \"df_delivery = pd.read_sql(query, engine)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"df_delivery.head()\"\n",
    "   ],\n",
